# Synology Monitor Package Build

After making changes to synology-monitor (including synology-monitor.py, package files, etc.), **always run the package build** so the SPK is up to date:

```bash
cd addons/synology-monitor/community-package && ./build-spk.sh
```

Output: `addons/synology-monitor/community-package/dist/synology-monitor-basic.spk`
